item.title: Tick Tock VIP - Ekstrak [Drum And Bass]
item.dc:creator: iammane
item.description:
I like it, the sweep in the beginning was a little jarring, is it supposed to be like a scratchy vinyl record sound? I like that. It was just unexpected.

I like the drums and the bass, you’ve got the aesthetic nailed classic drum and bass is more stripped down than a lot of the other genres we’re hearing around here. It almost sounds more like an organ which is hella cool. The changeup at like 3:13ish is awesome, didn’t expect it.

You (and I and many others) are going to benefit from the new drum stuff we’re getting, I’m really excited for it and I hope we’re gonna get more stuff suited to classic dnb (or at least the controls needed to get there).
